gH \text{ is fixed if and only if } g^{-1}hg\in H \text{ for all } h\in H,\text{ i.e. } g\in N_G(H). \text{ Since every subgroup of order } p \text{ in a group of order } p^2 \text{ is normal, } N_G(H)=G, \text{ and hence every coset in } G/H \text{ is fixed.}
